OL,3,CProstate screening only for 'most at
OL,4,Crisk' men, government says
OL,6,FOnly the most at-risk men will be
OL,7,Fscreened for prostate cancer after the
OL,8,Fhealth secretary accepted a
OL,9,Frecommendation from the UK National
OL,10,FScreening Committee (UKNSC).
OL,12,FThe announcement will come as a blow
OL,13,Fto campaigners who wanted every man to
OL,14,Fbe tested, but James Murray, who
OL,15,Freplaced Wes Streeting last month,
OL,16,Fsaid the government is "following the
OL,17,Fscience".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
