PN,31702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1780513862
OL,3,CProstate screening only for 'most at
OL,4,Crisk' men, government says
OL,6,FA final recommendation by the UKNSC,
OL,7,Fpublished last week, advised against
OL,8,Fscreening all men using the prostate-
OL,9,Fspecific antigen (PSA) blood test,
OL,10,Fsaying it is "likely to cause more
OL,11,Fharm than good".
OL,13,F"If you had a national screening
OL,14,Fprogramme for all men using current
OL,15,Fscreening techniques, most men who it
OL,16,Fwould bring up in those tests would
OL,17,Factually never go on to develop
OL,18,Fprostate. So that threatens their
OL,19,Flife, for instance," Murray said.
OL,26,@rD@NOUsD@OO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
