FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1780513862
OL,3,CProstate screening only for 'most at
OL,4,Crisk' men, government says
OL,6,F"They would, however, in many cases
OL,7,Fhave treatments and those treatments
OL,8,Fcan have really severe side effects,"
OL,9,Fhe added.
OL,11,FInstead, men with BRCA2 genetic
OL,12,Fmutations ` which puts them at far
OL,13,Fhigher risk of prostate cancer ` will
OL,14,Fbe tested every two years between the
OL,15,Fages of 45 and 61 if they have a
OL,16,Ffamily history of breast, ovarian,
OL,17,Fpancreatic or prostate cancers.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
