PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1780513862
OL,3,CProstate screening only for 'most at
OL,4,Crisk' men, government says
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FProstate cancer is more common,
OL,12,Fdevelops earlier and can be more
OL,13,Faggressive in this group.
OL,15,FOut of 100 men with a BRCA2 variant,
OL,16,Fbetween 21 and 35 of them will develop
OL,17,Fprostate cancer before the age of 80,
OL,18,Fso it is estimated that a "few
OL,19,Fthousand" men will be screened each
OL,20,Fyear.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
