FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1780513862
OL,3,CProstate screening only for 'most at
OL,4,Crisk' men, government says
OL,6,FThe UKNSC also recommended against
OL,7,Fscreening for other at-risk groups,
OL,8,Fincluding black men, saying there is
OL,9,F"ongoing uncertainty on whether
OL,10,Fscreening would cause more good than
OL,11,Fharm".
OL,13,FThere is some debate over the
OL,14,Freliability of the PSA test.
OL,16,FDr Ian Walker, director of policy at
OL,17,FCancer Research UK, said the decision
OL,18,Fwill be "disappointing for some" but
OL,19,Fis in line with evidence.
OL,26,@qD@AOUsD@EO]zD@IOUzD@`O]
