OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1780513862
OL,3,CProstate screening only for 'most at
OL,4,Crisk' men, government says
OL,6,FThe programme is expected to be rolled
OL,7,Fout in 2027.
OL,9,FWhile the health secretary accepted
OL,10,Fthe recommendation not to test all
OL,11,Fmen, he did announce a #20 million
OL,12,Finvestment into prostate cancer
OL,13,Fresearch and treatment.
OL,15,FThis includes funding to expand the
OL,16,FTransform trial, which is exploring
OL,17,Fthe best ways to screen for the
OL,18,Fdisease, to ensure it includes more
OL,19,Fblack men.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
