PN,31707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1780513862
OL,3,CProstate screening only for 'most at
OL,4,Crisk' men, government says
OL,6,FMurray described it as "a major step
OL,7,Fforward in how we tackle prostate
OL,8,Fcancer".
OL,10,F"By investing in research through
OL,11,Ftrials such as Transform, we're
OL,12,Fbuilding a fairer, more effective
OL,13,Fprostate cancer screening system for
OL,14,Fthe future."
OL,26,@rD@AOUvD@LO]
